transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you so much for calling Viagra, Escort Blue.

Speaker 2: How can I help you today?

Speaker 1: Yes, this is Michael Comerford,

Speaker 2: and you shipped me another refill that I didn't order.

Speaker 1: Okay, Michael, could I just get your date of birth,

Speaker 2: and I'll pull up your account and see what happened here?

Speaker 1: Okay, August 18th, 1948.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Okay, to confirm, this prescription

Speaker 2: was initially written in November,

Speaker 1: and that was for the 100 milligram Viagra, correct?

Speaker 2: Quantity of 25?

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: I see.

Speaker 2: So it looks like the doctor, based on the quantity,

Speaker 1: wrote it with refills every two months.

Speaker 2: Michael, you're not required or obligated

Speaker 1: to get this every two months.

Speaker 2: This is not a subscription, this is a prescription.

Speaker 1: It is perfectly adjustable, if you would like.

Speaker 2: Yeah, well, I'd like to,

Speaker 1: when I need it, call you and reorder it.

Speaker 2: I just don't want to,

Speaker 1: because I don't need that much,

Speaker 2: and you keep, you know, okay.

Speaker 1: No, it is perfect.

Speaker 2: So this prescription, when written, it comes with 12.

Speaker 1: And some patients do it monthly,

Speaker 2: some patients do it bi-monthly for convenience.

Speaker 1: If you would prefer to call in and place orders as needed,

Speaker 2: we can adjust your account that way.

Speaker 1: What I would do is I would put an extended pause on this,

Speaker 2: and then you can call in for any future orders.

Speaker 1: The remaining 10 are accessible at any time.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that would be great, then.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: I went ahead and did that for you.

Speaker 1: You're all set.

Speaker 2: Okay, so I'm all set?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir, you're all set.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you for your help.

Speaker 1: We appreciate it.

Speaker 2: Of course, happy to help, thank you.

Speaker 1: Bye.
